  <name>Glyph</name>
  <summary>Install fonts</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Glyph lets you install fonts from a catalog of thousands of fonts into your system for free.
      Browse and view previews of each font as you scroll.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Preview fonts without internet or installation.</li>
      <li>Search through thousands of fonts in various categories such as sans, mono etc.</li>
      <li>Install the latest font to your system.</li>
      <li>View the details of fonts such as the designer, license, files etc.</li>
      <li>Fonts fetched from Google Fonts Github repo with original quality.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.shonebinu">
